data.description: This charming home is an excellent opportunity for anyone looking for a cozy and comfortable living space. The natural color palette and fresh interior paint make this home inviting and warm. The living room is complete with a fireplace for cozy evenings. The kitchen is equipped with a nice backsplash and plenty of counter space. Flexible living space can be found in the other rooms of the house. The primary bathroom is equipped with double sinks and good under sink storage. Enjoy the outdoors with a fenced in backyard and a covered sitting area. This home has it all, and it won't last long. This home has been virtually staged to illustrate its potential.
